name: Generative Twist
description:
A new random Twist on every click.

Press 'A' to watch the animation of the current Twist
(can also be used to cancel the animation, the current one will be redrawn, and will be displayed on the screen)
Press 'S' to start a series of infinite animations (in black and white, ESC to exit)
Press 'C' to start a series of infinite animations (with colors, ESC to exit)

Colors can be set by pressing 1-5 (one color will be added to the black white palette)
1) default (black white)
2) Red
3) Green
4) Blue
5) Yellow
You can change the colors during an animation.
Last selected color will stay the active color for the next drawing (but for the animations.

Written in JavaScript
